<h1 align="CENTER">Frozen Yeast TRAFO Protocol</h1>

<p align="CENTER"><img src="./Frozen Yeast TRAFO Protocol_files/bluebar.GIF" align="BOTTOM" width="560" height="11" naturalsizeflag="3"></p>
